e%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20changed%20my%20life.%20I%20remember%20thinking%20in%20California%20that%20that%20was%20the%20end.%20I've%20already%20been%20married.%20It%20didn't%20work%20out.%20I'm%20never%20going%20to%20have%20a%20stable%20job.%20I'm%20never%20going%20to%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20support%20myself%20and%20my%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20%241%2C750%20for%20rent%20in%20a%20crappy%20little%20apartment%20in%20California.%20Now%2C%20three%20years%20later%2C%20my%20whole%20payment%2C%20including%20mortgage%20and%20property%20taxes%20is%20%241%2C800%20a%20month%20for%20my%20three-bedroom%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20house%20changed%20everything.%20It's%20not%20just%20a%20home.%20This%20is%20my%20future.%20This%20is%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20give%20my%20son%20when%20he's%20old%20and%20I%20pass%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Janelle%20Crossan%20was%20able%20to%20purchase%20a%20home%20in%20Texas%20after%20living%20in%20an%20apartment%20in%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652096a86561dd877e73e52b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221142%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJanelle%20Crossan%20was%20able%20to%20purchase%20a%20home%20in%20Texas%20after%20living%20in%20an%20apartment%20in%20California.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Janelle%20Crossan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20son%20turned%20into%20an%20immediate%20Texan.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20loves%20it%20in%20Texas.%20We%20moved%20here%20right%20when%20he%20turned%20five%20so%20most%20of%20his%20memories%20are%20now%20here.%20He%20loves%20being%20outdoors%20and%20going%20on%20camping%20trips%20and%20tubing%20in%20the%20river.%20He's%20taking%20archery.%20The%20school%20system%20here%20is%20much%20better%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20the%20South%20and%20its%20hospitality.%20The%20people%20are%20very%20friendly.%20You%20can%20talk%20to%20anyone%20on%20the%20street%20and%20probably%20trust%20them.%20I%20still%20find%20it%20a%20bit%20difficult%20to%20make%20friends.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20why%20that%20is.%20Maybe%20I%20really%20just%20am%20from%20another%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolitically%2C%20I'm%20a%20strong%20libertarian.%20That%20wasn't%20something%20that%20was%20accepted%20in%20California.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20couldn't%20be%20true%20to%20myself%20in%20California%20because%20I%20wasn't%20accepted%20for%20who%20I%20was%20and%20what%20I%20believed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Texas%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-california-texas-conservative-affordable-realtor-helps-others-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20big%20part%20of%20the%20culture%20is%20independence%20and%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20being%20responsible%20for%20yourself%20while%20still%20having%20empathy%20for%20others.%20I%20can%20share%20my%20opinions%20here.%20That's%20freedom%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Janelle%20Crossan's%20son%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20a%20river.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6520964e9f7ca8b2bbdcb7e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20Braunfels%2C%20Texas%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20cities%20in%20the%20country.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Janelle%20Crossan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EBut%20there%20are%20also%20some%20bad%20things.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20the%20gun%20culture%20here.%20I%20like%20that%20guns%20are%20more%20rare%20in%20California.%20But%20it's%20something%20I've%20had%20to%20accept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20here%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwinter-snow-storm-blackout-texas-damages-could-near-50-billion-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20big%20ice%20storm%20hit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20was%20sc