cal%20averages.%20The%20delinquency%20rate%20for%20consumer%20credit%20card%20loans%20is%202.58%25%2C%20which%20is%20a%20full%20percentage%20point%20above%20its%202021%20low%2C%20but%20still%2031%25%20below%2032-year%20average%20of%203.74%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221130%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Delinquency%20rates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652053449f7ca8b2bbdc5335%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22705%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYCharts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20rising%20interest%20rates%20only%20impacts%20new%20loans%20or%20refinancings%2C%20and%20just%20over%2075%25%20of%20mortgage%20holders%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redfin.com%2Fnews%2Fhigh-mortgage-rates-lock-in-homeowners-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20interest%20rate%20below%205%25.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It's%20the%20same%20story%20for%20corporate%20debt%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Savita%20Subramanian%2C%20who%20highlighted%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Feconomy-outlook-us-recession-delayed-corporate-debt-binge-low-rates-2023-7%5C%22%3E76%25%20of%20debt%20held%20by%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20companies%20is%20long-term%20and%20fixed%20at%20low%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20perhaps%20the%20most%20commonly%20talked-about%20risk%20of%20the%20consumer%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20is%20the%20idea%20that%20they%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-consumers-spend-down-excess-pandemic-savings-2023-8%5C%22%3Espent%20down%20all%20of%20their%20excess%20savings%20from%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20so%20common%20for%20economists%20to%20mention%20that%20the%20excess%20savings%20have%20run%20out%20that%20it%20ha