%20are%20still%20assessing%20what%20concrete%20impact%20it%20will%20have%20on%20their%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20time%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20AI%20can%20make%20much%20of%20the%20work%20easier%2C%20less%20manual%20and%20more%20impactful%2C%20but%20in%20this%20in-between%20period%2C%20I%20talk%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20mostly%20just%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20end%20is%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECristina%20Diezhandino%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20Diageo%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227338%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Head%20shot%20of%20Cristina%20Diezhandino%2C%20Diageo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65170e953fb8f400198ad811%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECristina%20Diezhandino%2C%20Diageo%3Cp%3EDiageo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDiezhandino%20has%20been%20Diageo's%20CMO%20since%20July%2C%202020%2C%20having%20held%20a%20range%20of%20roles%20across%20the%20company's%20brands%20since%202006.%20Previously%2C%20she%20held%20senior%20marketing%20roles%20at%20Allied%20Domecq%20and%20Unilever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Cannes%20Lions%20in%202023%2C%20Diezhandino%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-cannes-lions-are-brands-brave-enough-2023-6%5C%22%3Ea%20panelist%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Insider's%20launch%20event%20for%20CMO%20Insider%2C%20with%20the%20session%20titled%20%26quot%3BIs%20Your%20Brand%20Brave%20Enough%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20incredibly%20proud%20to%20be%20able%20to%20speak%20to%20so%20much%20work%20our%20brands%20have%20done%20in%20'being%20brave'%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.diageo.com%2Fen%2Fnews-and-media%2Fstories%2F2023%2Freflections-on-cannes-lions-2023-from-our-chief-marketing-officer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20afterward%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20J%26amp%3BB'