EAP%20Photo%2FAndrew%20Harnik%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EOhio%20Rep.%20Jim%20Jordan%20is%20a%20top%20contender%20in%20the%20race%20for%20House%20speaker%20after%20Kevin%20McCarthy's%20ouster%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EJordan%20has%20repeatedly%20voted%20against%20measures%20authorizing%20continued%20US%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20war%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHis%20ascension%20to%20the%20speakership%20could%20also%20hinge%20on%20making%20a%20deal%20with%20far-right%20Republicans%20to%20curb%20US%20security%20assistance.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20race%20to%20replace%20Rep.%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20as%20speaker%20of%20the%20House%20is%20heating%20up%20%E2%80%94%20and%20US%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20may%20be%20the%20biggest%20issue%20on%20the%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20contenders%20for%20the%20spot%20are%20Ohio%20Rep.%20Jim%20Jordan%20and%20Louisiana%20Rep.%20Steve%20Scalise.%20The%20two%20Republicans%20agree%20on%20a%20slew%20of%20issues%2C%20but%20they're%20sharply%20divided%20on%20the%20question%20of%20how%20much%20security%20assistance%20the%20US%20should%20send%20to%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%94%20if%20any%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20as%20it%20continues%20fighting%20off%20Russian%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20Jordan%20%E2%80%94%20a%20member%20of%20the%20far-right%20House%20Freedom%20Caucus%20%E2%80%94%20wins%20the%20battle%20for%20speaker%2C%20it%20could%20signal%20the%20end%20of%20American%20aid%20to%20its%20embattled%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ohio%20lawmaker%20has%20made%20no%20secret%20of%20his%20opposition%20to%20continued%20US%20support%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20consistently%20voted%20against%20measures%20that%20would%20increase%20security%20assistance%20to%20the%20country%2C%20and%20he%20received%20a%20score%20of%20%26quot%3BF%26quot%3B%20regarding%20US%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%20from%20the%20conservative%20group%20Defending%20Democracy%20Together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20told%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20pressing%20issue%20on%20Americans'%20minds%20is%20not%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20is%20the%20border%20situation%20and%20crime%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20everybody%20knows%20that.%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20FOX%20%26amp%3B%20Friends%20this%20week%20that%20he%20wanted%20more%20details%20on%20how%20Ukraine%20would%20use%20the%20aid%20%26quot%3Bbefore%20we%20even%20think%20about%20sending%20more%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublican%20calls%20to%20abandon%20Kyiv%20aren't%20new%3B%20indeed%2C%20Ukrainian%20lawmakers%20and%20US%20national%20security%20experts%20have%20closely%20watched%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20GOP-controlled%20House%20since%20the%20party%20won%20control%20of%20the%20chamber%20in%20last%20year's%20midterm%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20signs%20were%20building%20even%20before%20the%20midterms.%20In%20April%202022%2C%2010%20House%20Republicans%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%2264be65b8bb74305136beda19e33de0ab%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F10-republicans-vote-against-military-equipment-ukraine-gaetz-greene-gosar-2022-4%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evoted%20against%20a%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0allowing%20the%20Biden%20administration%20to%20more%20easily%20lend%20military%20equipment%20to%20Ukraine.%20The%20following%20month%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%220ad2a8249ad03cbb86f140c4b371c179%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fhouse%2F3483993-house-approves-40b-in-aid-for-ukraine-57-republicans-vote-no%2F%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E57%20House%20Republicans%3C%2Fa%3E%20voted%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20nearly%20%2440%20billion%20aid%20package%20for%20Ukraine.%20Both%20measures%20ultimately%20passed%20the%20chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20GOP%20Rep.%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20of%20California%20was%20elected%20speaker%20after%20a%20painstaking%20uphill%20battle%2C%20concerns%20about%20whether%20the%20US%20had%20the%20political%20will%20to%20continue%20backing%20Kyiv%20ratcheted%20up%20a%20notch.%20After%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20rounds%20of%20voting%2C%20McCarthy%20caved%20to%20a%20list%20of%20demands%20from%20a%20far-right%20faction%20of%20GOP%20lawmakers%20led%20by%20Florida%20Rep.%20Matt%20Gaetz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaetz%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20McCarthy%20at%20the%20time%20that%20he%20may%20be%20speaker%2C%20but%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22e77db7d48a7b3c8faae3839997c30646%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F01%2F29%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fmatt-gaetz.html%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20name%20only%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20this%20week%2C%20he%20followed%20through%20on%20that%20threat%20by%20engineering%20McCarthy's%20ouster%20after%20the%20California%20lawmaker%20worked%20with%20Democrats%20to%20pass%20a%20temporary%20funding%20bill%20to%20avert%20a%20government%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Jordan%20were%20elected%20speaker%2C%20he%20could%20face%20the%20same%20pressure%20from%20his%20intraparty%20colleagues%20that%20McCarthy%20did.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnewsletters%2Fnational-security-daily%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20Politico%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jordan's%20ascension%20to%20the%20speakership%20could%20hinge%20on%20making%20a%20deal%20with%20Gaetz%20and%20his%20far-right%20cohort%20to%20curb%20US%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%20And%20he%20could%20also%20get%20the%20boot%20if%20he%20doesn't%20make%20good%20on%20those%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20get%20some%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20GOP%20Rep.%20Don%20Bacon%20told%20Politico%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20Ukraine-centric%20quid%20pro%20quo.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20GOP%20pulls%20the%20rug%20out%20from%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%20prevails%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20disgusting%20legacy%20the%20party%20will%20own%20for%20decades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjim-jordan-house-speaker-ukraine-aid-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696619778000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63cc2e99fcc41d0018a398bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjim-jordan-house-speaker-ukraine-aid-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jordan%20has%20repeatedly%20voted%20against%20increasing%20security%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20his%20ascension%20to%20the%20speakership%20could%20hinge%20on%20a%20deal%20with%20far-right%20Republicans%20promising%20to%20curb%20US%20aid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ssheth%40businessinsider.com%20(Sonam%20Sheth)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjim-jordan-house-speaker-ukraine-aid-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mother%20pleads%20guilty%20to%20accidentally%20killing%20daughter%20while%20shooting%20at%20dog%20attacking%20kittens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696619280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-oklahoma-shooter_6311706.png%3F20231006204037%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmother-pleads-guilty-to-accidentally-killing-daughter-while-shooting-at-dog-attacking-kittens-12978596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20has%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20accidentally%20killing%20her%20teenage%20daughter%20w