0security%20resources%20expended%20for%20Trump%20to%20attend%20the%20first%20three%20days%20of%20testimony%2C%20special%20arrangements%20for%20press%20and%20public%20access%2C%20and%20the%20impact%20that%20a%20delay%20would%20have%20on%20witnesses%20who've%20cleared%20their%20schedules%20to%20testify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defendants%20can%20continue%20to%20try%20to%20delay%20and%20stall%2C%20but%20the%20evidence%20is%20clear%2C%20and%20our%20case%20is%20strong.%20We%20are%20confident%20justice%20will%20prevail%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngoron%20ruled%20last%20week%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-new-york-judge-finds-business-2023-9%5C%22%3ETrump%20committed%20fraud%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20years%20as%20he%20built%20the%20real%20estate%20empire%20that%20vaulted%20him%20to%20fame%20and%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%2C%20ruling%20on%20the%20top%20claim%20in%20James'%20lawsuit%2C%20found%20that%20Trump%20routinely%20deceived%20banks%2C%20insurers%20and%20others%20by%20exaggerating%20the%20value%20of%20assets%20on%20his%20annual%20financial%20statements%2C%20which%20were%20used%20in%20making%20deals%20and%20securing%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20denied%20wrongdoing%2C%20arguing%20that%20some%20of%20his%20assets%20are%20worth%20far%20more%20than%20what's%20listed%20on%20the%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Engoron%20issued%20an%20order%20setting%20procedures%20for%20enforcing%20his%20ruling.%20He%20gave%20both%20sides%20until%20Oct.%2026%20to%20submit%20names%20of%20potential%20receivers%20and%20gave%20Trump%20and%20other%20defendants%20seven%20days%20to%20provide%20a%20court-appointed%20monitor%2C%20retired%20federal%20judge%20Barbara%20Jones%2C%20with%20a%20list%20of%20all%20entities%20covered%20by%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20ordered%20the%20defendants%20to%20give%20Jones%20advance%20notice%20of%20any%20application%20for%20new%20business%20