cations%20sometimes%20lag%20between%20a%20phone%20and%20the%20watch.%3Cp%3ERick%20Stella%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Watch%206%20Classic%20offers%20solid%20smartwatch%20functionality%20but%20I%20did%20find%20it%20to%20be%20oddly%20laggy%20at%20times.%20I%20would%20often%20feel%20the%20buzz%20of%20a%20notification%20on%20my%20phone%20and%20when%20I%20raised%20the%20watch%20to%20see%20what%20it%20was%2C%20there%20was%20a%20delay%20of%20several%20seconds.%20While%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20this%20is%20a%20dealbreaker%2C%20it%20does%20slightly%20alter%20the%20overall%20experience.%20With%20almost%20any%20other%20smartwatch%20I've%20worn%2C%20I'm%20used%20to%20notifications%20popping%20up%20the%20exact%20moment%20they%20vibrate%20on%20my%20smartphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20the%20Watch%206%20Classic%20is%20a%20quality%20smartwatch.%20Its%20use%20of%20Wear%20OS%204%20makes%20navigating%20the%20interface%20smooth%20and%20intuitive%2C%20and%20even%20first-time%20Android%20smartwatch%20users%20shouldn't%20encounter%20a%20steep%20learning%20curve.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watch%20also%20allows%20for%20quick%20responses%20to%20texts%20and%20emails%2C%20and%20I%20found%20these%20suggested%20prompts%20to%20be%20legitimately%20useful.%20I%20especially%20enjoyed%20answering%20phone%20calls%20directly%20on%20the%20watch%2C%20which%20I%20used%20often%20when%20my%20phone%20wasn't%20nearby%20or%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20fetch%20it%20from%20my%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20data%20customization%20screen%20on%20a%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%206%20Classic.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65202fec6561dd877e731cb7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221204%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20screen%20customization%20options%20for%20displaying%20whatever%20kind%20of%20data%20you%20want.%3Cp%3ERick%20Stella%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E