compared%20to%20using%20the%20touchscreen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20its%20GPS%20syncing%20just%20isn't%20very%20accurate%20or%20fast.%20Not%20only%20would%20it%20take%20around%20a%20minute%20to%20sync%20but%20the%20tracking%20data%20was%20often%20inconsistent.%20To%20the%20casual%20wearer%2C%20this%20may%20not%20matter%20all%20that%20much%20but%20to%20someone%20training%20for%20an%20event%2C%20it%20can%20really%20throw%20them%20off.%20Let%20me%20explain%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%20the%20watch's%20GPS%20would%20be%20within%20.05%20miles%20of%20my%20standard%20mile%20time%20and%20distance%2C%20while%20other%20days%20it%20would%20be%20closer%20to%20.1%20miles%20or%20more.%20While%20you'd%20like%20to%20see%20accuracy%20closer%20to%20.01%2C%20.05%20isn't%20terrible.%20But%20for%20it%20to%20be%20off%20by%20as%20much%20as%20a%20tenth%20of%20a%20mile%20is%20a%20significant%20discrepancy.%20This%20spells%20the%20difference%20between%20me%20seeing%20that%20I%20ran%20an%20eight-minute%20mile%20when%20I%20really%20ran%20a%20mile%20closer%20to%20seven%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20accurate%20activity%20tracking%20you're%20after%20in%20a%20Galaxy%20Watch%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-watch5-pro-review%5C%22%3EWatch%205%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20far%20better%20option%20with%20more%20reliable%20GPS.%20The%20Watch%206%20Classic's%20shortcomings%20as%20a%20fitness%20tracker%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20dealbreaker%20to%20the%20ordinary%20active%20user%20but%20should%20cause%20advanced%20athletes%2C%20or%20anyone%20training%20for%20a%20specific%20race%2C%20to%20think%20twice%20about%20using%20it%20as%20their%20go-to%20training%20wearable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Health%20features%5C%22%3EHealth%20tracking%20is%20a%20major%20highlight%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20body%20composition%20app%20screen%20on%20a%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%206%20Classic.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6520306e9f7ca8b2bbdbf0f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221204%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20body%20composition%20app%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20health%20tools%20the%20Watch%206%20Classic%20offers.%3Cp%3ERick%20Stella%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Watch%206%20Classic%20has%20a%20number%20of%20health%20tools%20I%20use%20daily%2C%20including%20its%20in-depth%20sleep%20tracker%20and%2C%20my%20personal%20favorite%2C%20the%20body%20composition%20analyzer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20body%20composition%20analyzer%2C%20the%20Watch%206%20Classic%20assessed%20certain%20data%20like%20my%20body%20fat%20percentage%2C%20muscle%20mass%2C%20and%20skeletal%20muscle%20all%20via%20an%20easy-to-use%2C%2015-second%20process%20where%20I%20put%20my%20middle%20and%20ring%20finger%20on%20the%20watch's%20side%20buttons.%20Although%20the%20data%20isn't%20considered%20medical-grade%2C%20and%20shouldn't%20be%20viewed%20as%20100%20percent%20accurate%2C%20I%20did%20like%20that%20it%20provided%20another%20way%20for%20me%20to%20track%20my%20fitness%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20the%20sleep%20tracker%20often%2C%20too%2C%20and%20it%20provided%20similar%20data%20compared%20to%20the%20Watch%205%20Pro.%20While%20it%20tracks%20the%20different%20sleep%20zones%20I%20entered%20each%20night%20(like%20REM%2C%20deep%2C%20and%20light)%2C%20the%20most%20useful%20part%20was%20its%20sleep%20coaching%20which%20provided%20guidance%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20my%20habits%20and%20get%20the%20most%20rest.%20Some%20days%20it%20recommended%20I%20go%20to%20sleep%20earlier%20while%20on%20others%20it%20would%20offer%20things%20I%20could%20do%20throughout%20the%20day%20to%20sleep%20better%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Compatibility%5C%22%3EThe%20best%20experience%20requires%20the%20use%20of%20a%20Samsung%20phone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompatibility%20has%20long%20been%20a%20weakness%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%2C%20and%20the%20Watch%206%20Classic%20is%20no%20different.%20I%20tested%20the%20watch%20using%20a%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20S21%20and%20a%20Google%20Pixel%207%20and%20although%20the%20watch%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20compatible%20with%20any%20smartphone%20running%20Android%208.0%20or%20later%2C%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20were%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20there%20were%20syncing%20issues.%20With%20the%20S21%2C%20the%20Watch%206%20Classic%20synced%20a%20Bluetooth%20connection%20right%20away%20and%20the%20setup%20process%20was%20smooth%20and%20easy.%20The%20Pixel%207%20was%20the%20opposite.%20Syncing%20a%20connection%20required%20several%20attempts%20as%20the%20initial%20setup%20process%20failed%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20got%20the%20watch%20synced%20with%20the%20Pixel%207%2C%20I%20then%20needed%20to%20download%20a%20wholly%20different%20app%20than%20what%20I%20used%20with%20the%20S21.%20While%20the%20S21%20uses%20the%20Samsung%20Health%20Monitor%2C%20the%20Pixel%207%20requires%20the%20Galaxy%20Wearable%20app%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20pales%20in%20comparison.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20both%20centralize%20your%20health%20and%20fitness%20data%2C%20like%20workouts%2C%20steps%20taken%2C%20and%20calories%20burned%2C%20the%20Galaxy%20Wearable%20app%20is%20devoid%20of%20a%20few%20key%20health%20features%20native%20to%20the%20Watch%206%20Classic.%20These%20include%20blood%20pressure%20monitoring%20and%20access%20to%20the%20ECG%20app.%20This%20meant%20I%20just%20didn't%20have%20access%20to%20either%20while%20using%20the%20Pixel%207.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20that%2C%20I%20felt%20as%20though%20the%20Pixel%207%20delivered%20a%20watered-down%20version%20of%20the%20Watch%206%20Classic%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20health-tracking%20capability.%20For%20those%20wanting%20a%20full-featured%20health%20tracker%2C%20know%20that%20the%20absolute%20b