itrary%20and%20unprecedented%2C%20and%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20done%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdictates%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20further%20their%20political%20motives%20and%20vested%20interest%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20pointed%20to%20several%20other%20first-time%20MPs%20living%20in%20such%20accommodations%20and%20said%20that%20he%20will%20be%20taking%20%E2%80%9Cappropriate%20legal%20action%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECourt%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Chadha%20was%20given%20a%20Type%206%20bungalow%20in%20July%20last%20year%20and%20had%20requested%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20for%20a%20bigger%2C%20Type%207%20accommodation%2C%20which%20was%20allotted%20to%20him%20in%20September%20that%20year.%20In%20March%2C%20however%2C%20the%20secretariat%20had%20cancelled%20the%20allotment%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20first-time%20MP%20was%20not%20entitled%20to%20a%20bungalow%20of%20that%20grade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20MP%20was%20asked%20to%20vacate%20the%20bungalow%2C%20which%20is%20in%20central%20Delhi's%20Pandara%20Road%2C%20and%20had%20moved%20Delhi's%20Patiala%20House%20court%20against%20the%20order.%20The%20court%20had%20granted%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20April%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELifting%20the%20stay%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Patiala%20House%20court%20said%20Mr%20Chadha%20could%20not%20claim%20an%20absolute%20right%20to%20occupy%20the%20bungalow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiff%20cannot%20claim%20that%20he%20has%20an%20absolute%20right%20to%20continue%20to%20occupy%20the%20accommodation%20during%20his%20entire%20tenure%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20The%20allotment%20of%20Government%20accommodation%20is%20only%20a%20privilege%20given%20to%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20he%20has%20no%20vested%20right%20to%20continue%20to%20occupy%20the%20same%20even%20after%20the%20cancellation%20of%20allotment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20in%20its%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20remarked%20that%20the%20argument%20that%20the%20allotment%2C%20once%20made%2C%20cannot%20be%20cancelled%20under%20any%20circumstances%20during%20the%20MP's%20entire%20tenure%20%26quot%3Bdeserves%20rejection%26quot%3B.%20The%20court%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%2C%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Mr%20Chadha%20has%20no%20vested%20right%20in%20the%20accommodation%20and%20his%20status%20was%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20a%20licensee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Above%20His%20Grade'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20housing%20committee%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Type%207%20bungalow%20was%20above%20Mr%20Chadha's%20grade%20as%20a%20first-time%20MP%20and%20that%20such%20accommodations%20are%20usually%20assigned%20to%20former%20Union%20Ministers%2C%20former%20governors%20or%20former%20chief%20ministers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20head%20of%20the%20committee%20had%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20BJP%20MP%20Radha%20Mohan%20Das%20had%20been%20moved%20from%20a%20Type%207%20to%20a%20Type%205%20bungalow%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20Notice'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Mr%20Chadha%20said%20he%20has%20been%20wrongfully%20targeted%20and%20victimised%2C%20and%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20for%20trying%20to%20stifle%20political%20criticism%20from%20MPs%20like%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cancellation%20of%20my%20duly%20allotted%20official%20accommodation%20was%20arbitrary%20without%20any%20notice%20to%20me.%20It%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20more%20than%2070%20years%20of%20history%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20a%20sitting%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20removed%20from%20his%20duly%20allotted%20accommodation%20where%20he%20has%20been%20residing%20for%20a%20while%20and%20more%20than%204%20years%20of%20his%20tenure%20are%20still%20remaining%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20leader%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Chadha%20claimed%20there%20were%20many%20irregularities%20in%20the%20order%20and%20that%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Secretariat%20were%20in%20clear%20contravention%20of%20rules%20and%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20MP%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20manner%20of%20the%20entire%20exercise%20leaves%20me%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20believe%20that%20these%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20dictates%20of%20BJP%20to%20further%20their%20political%20motives%20and%20vested%20interest%20in%20order%20to%20scuttle%20and%20stifle%20the%20political%20criticism%20raised%20by%20vocal%20parliamentarians%20like%20me.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%2C%20along%20with%20my%20suspension%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20which%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20leaves%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20target%20vocal%20Members%20of%20Parliament.%20This%20amounts%20to%20unwarranted%20interference%20in%20the%20due%20discharge%20of%20their%20functions%20as%20the%20Representatives%20of%20the%20House%20and%20hits%20a%20rock%20bottom%20of%20vendetta%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20buttress%20his%20claim%2C%20Mr%20Chadha%20pointed%20out%20that%20many%20of%20his%20neighbours%20were%20first-time%20MPs%20who%20had%20been%20allotted%20the%20exact%20same%20accommodation%20above%20their%20entitlement.%20He%20took%20the%20names%20of%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Danish%20Ali%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Rakesh%20Sinha%20and%20former%20MP%20Roopa%20Ganguly%2C%20who%20was%20the%20previous%20occupant%20of%20the%20bungalow%20that%20had%20been%20allotted%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterestingly%2C%20about%20118%20out%20of%20240%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Members%20are%20living%20in%20accommodations%20above%20their%20entitlement%20but%20selectively%20targeting%20and%20interfering%20with%20vocal%20representatives%2C%20who%20are%20giving%20a%20strong%20opposition%20to%20BJP%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20and%20maintaining%20a%20healthy%20democracy%2C%20is%20a%20sorry%20state%20of%20affairs%20for%20the%20nation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MP%20rued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20trial%20court%20had%20initially%20accepted%20my%20plea%20and%20granted%20me%20interim%20relief.%20It%20has%20now%20returned%20my%20case%20on%20a%20legal%20technicality%2C%20which%20I%20am%20legally%20advised%20to%20state%20is%20based%20on%20an%20incorrect%20understanding%20of%20the%20law.%20I%20will%20be%20taking%20appropriate%20action%20in%20law%20in%20due%20course.%20Needless%20to%20state%2C%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20raise%20the%20voice%20of%20people%20of%20Punjab%20and%20India%20fearlessly%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20costs%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696612320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5g4hlugs_raghav-chadha-ani_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-raghav-chadha-be-evicted-from-government-bungalow-what-court-said-4457623%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20setback%20for%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%2C%20a%20Delhi%20court%20has%20ruled%20that%20he%20has%20no%20right%20to%20continue%20to%20occupy%20the%20government%20bungalow%20given%20to%20him%20after%20the%20allotment%20was%20cancelled.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-raghav-chadha-be-evicted-from-government-bungalow-what-court-said-4457623%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-raghav-chadha-be-evicted-from-government-bungalow-what-court-said-4457623%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-raghav-chadha-be-evicted-from-government-bungalow-what-court-said-4457623%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BG