President%20in%20Muizzu%2C%20Fear%20of%20Repression%20Looms%20Large%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01175145%2FScreenshot-2023-10-01-at-5.49.11%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ETwelve%20years%20ago%2C%20Daniel%20Bosley%20came%20across%20an%20ad%20from%20the%20Maldivian%20high%20commission%20in%20London%2C%20which%20said%20it%20was%20looking%20for%20interns.%20The%20Englishman%2C%20in%20his%20twenties%20and%20desperate%20for%20a%20job%2C%20lunged%20at%20it%2C%20only%20to%20realise%20that%20even%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20international%20relations%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20equipped%20him%20with%20enough%20knowledge%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Maldives%20was%20certainly%20synonymous%20with%20some%20turquoise%20corner%20of%20my%20grey%20matter%20with%20unattainable%20luxury%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20later.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20else%20was%20there%20to%20know%20about%20the%20place%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20really%20get%20into%20it%20though%2C%20the%20Maldives%20reveals%20itself%20as%20a%20riveting%20study%20of%20contrasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20an%20Islamic%20republic%20where%20conservatism%20ends%20at%20the%20shores%20of%20its%20luxury%20resorts.%20A%20laidback%20culture%20that%20has%20the%20distinction%20of%20sending%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lowyinstitute.org%2Fthe-interpreter%2Fmaldives-legacy-islamic-state%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFrom%25202014%2520to%25202018%252C%2520more%2Ca%2520country%2520of%2520only%2520500%252C000.%5C%22%3Ehighest%20per%20capita%20recruits%20to%20ISIS%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20so%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20rising%20sea%20levels%20that%20scientists%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20would%20survive%20beyond%20this%20century.%20Yet%2C%20such%20existential%20issues%20only%20appear%20as%20a%20footnote%20in%20the%20political%20discourse%2C%20as%20the%20recently%20concluded%20presidential%20elections%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20material%20so%20rich%20that%20you%20could%20write%20a%20book%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20Bosley%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-politics-came-full-circle-in-the-maldives%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EDescent%3A%20A%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20memoir%20of%20the%20untold%20Maldives%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20an%20account%20of%20the%2010%20years%20that%20Bosley%20spent%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20archipelago.%20After%20his%20internship%20(he%20did%20land%20it)%2C%20he%20flew%20to%20Mal%C3%A9%20and%20joined%20the%20%3Cem%3EMaldives%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20journalist%20and%20then%20as%20an%20editor.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20be%20a%20writer%20for%20a%20host%20of%20magazines%2C%20before%20launching%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwothousandisles.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Two%20Thousand%20Isles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20unique%20website%20chronicling%20the%20rarely%20told%20slices%20of%20the%20island%20life%2C%20with%20his%20Maldivian%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20book%20is%20a%20loving%20and%20roving%20tale%20of%20this%20unique%20country.%20It%E2%80%99s%20deeply%20researched%20and%20masterfully%20told.%20And%20it%20is%20among%20the%20most%20perceptive%20books%20on%20the%20islands%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20314px)%2085vw%2C%20314px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05174917%2F0.89526800_1694829326_daniel-bosley.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05174917%2F0.89526800_1694829326_daniel-bosley.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05174917%2F0.89526800_1694829326_daniel-bosley-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05174917%2F0.89526800_1694829326_daniel-bosley-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678468%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDaniel%20Bosley.%20Photo%3A%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20also%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Maldives%20is%20set%20to%20witness%20a%20change%20in%20government.%20President-elect%20Dr.%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20stand-in%20for%20Abdulla%20Yameen%2C%20the%20ex-president%20convicted%20for%20overseeing%20the%20biggest%20corruption%20scandal%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20country.%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20rule%20saw%20the%20press%20censored%2C%20Islamic%20extremism%20rise%2C%20political%20dissenters%20exiled%2C%20and%20India-Maldives%20relations%20deteriorate.%20Muizzu%20had%20sworn%20to%20release%20Yameen%20and%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-biggest-stakeholder-indian-ocean-region-advisor-muizzu%5C%22%3EIndian%20troops%3C%2Fa%3E%20stationed%20in%20the%20country%20if%20elected.%20And%20it%20seems%20to%20have%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20spoke%20to%20Bosley%20about%20his%20book%20and%20what%20recent%20political%20developments%20mean%20for%20India.%20Excerpts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20your%20book%2C%20you%20recall%20instances%20of%20how%20often%20may%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20understand%20the%20country%20beyond%20its%20cliches.%20What%20are%20people%20missing%20out%20when%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20to%20know%20the%20Maldives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20missing%20something%20that%20cannot%20be%20seen%20anywhere%20else%20on%20earth%20and%2C%20sadly%2C%20something%20that%20may%20not%20exist%20at%20all%20in%20a%20few%20decades%E2%80%99%20time.%20Maldivians%20have%20been%20living%20on%20these%20islands%20for%20at%20least%202%2C500%20years%2C%20carving%20out%20a%20unique%20civilisation%20millennia%20before%20the%20world%20even%20knew%20they%20were%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20resorts%20are%20certainly%20mind-%20and%20budget-blowing%2C%20but%20perfection%20can%20also%20be%20bland.%20There%20will%20always%20be%20luxury%20resorts%20somewhere%2C%20but%20there%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20another%20Dhivehi%20Raajje.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20country%20has%20high%20literacy%20rates%2C%20including%20in%20spoken%20and%20written%20English.%20Yet%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20ever%20been%20foreigners%20who%20deep-dive%20into%20its%20history%2Fculture%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20world.%20Why%20do%20you%20think%20that%20is%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20missionaries%2C%20castaways%2C%20explorers%2C%20colonialists%20or%20journalists%20who%E2%80%99ve%20written%20about%20the%20Maldives%20%E2%80%93%20usually%20while%20passing%20through.%20Before%20tourism%2C%20Maldivians%20were%20taught%20to%20be%20suspicious%20of%20outsiders%2C%20and%20the%20official%20narrative%20of%20history%20has%20been%20tightly%20controlled%20by%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHigh%20literacy%20rates%20are%20a%20relatively%20modern%20phenomenon%2C%20but%20writing%20openly%20and%20honestly%20from%20within%20any%20small%20and%20highly%20politicised%20community%20is%20still%20difficult.%20When%20a%20country%20relies%20on%20a%20pristine%20image%20for%20its%20livelihood%2C%20this%20further%20exacerbates%20the%20problem%20and%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20recent%20past%20has%20shown%20that%20talking%20about%20life%20beyond%20the%20resorts%20can%20be%20deadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20also%20found%20that%20%E2%80%93%20like%20many%20people%20everywhere%20%E2%80%93%20most%20Maldivians%20simply%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%20how%20fascinating%20their%20own%20society%20and%20culture%20are%20to%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDr.%20Muizzu%20has%20had%20a%20chequered%20record%20as%20the%20housing%20minister%2C%20and%20Yameen%20was%20convicted%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20biggest%20corruption%20scandal%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Maldives.%20How%20did%20the%20two%20manage%20to%20secure%20an%20electoral%20victory%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20feels%20like%20an%20election%20lost%2C%20rather%20than%20an%20election%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYameen%E2%80%99s%20term%20between%202013%20and%202018%20was%20calamitous%2C%20with%20opposition%20leaders%20thrown%20into%20jail%2C%20his%20vice%20president%20arrested%20for%20attempting%20to%20assassinate%20him%20and%20two%20states%20of%20emergency%20declared.%20It%20felt%20like%20the%20country%20was%20slipping%20into%20autocratic%20anarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01175213%2FF7Wa7ZlacAAu3nj.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01175213%2FF7Wa7ZlacAAu3nj.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01175213%2FF7Wa7ZlacAAu3nj-300x162.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01175213%2FF7Wa7ZlacAAu3nj-1024x553.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677823%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMaldivian%20president-elect%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20meets%20outgoing%20president%20Ibu%20Solih%2C%20October%201%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40Muizzu2O23%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20outgoing%20President%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20since%202018%20has%20been%20so%20disappointing%20that%20it%20eventually%20split%20his%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20(MDP)%20down%20the%20middle.%20The%20ebbing%20influence%20of%20the%20MDP%E2%80%99s%20former%20figurehead%2C%20Mohamed%20Nasheed%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20him%20from%20acting%20as%20a%20one-man%20opposition%20from%20the%20Majlis%20speaker%E2%80%99s%20chair%2C%20calling%20out%20the%20government%20for%20its%20record%20on%20corruption%20and%20extremism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20bitter%20was%20this%20rift%20that%20after%20leaving%20to%20form%20a%20new%20party%2C%20this%20clutch%20of%20MDP%20defectors%20still%20refused%20to%20endorse%20Solih%20in%20the%20run-off%2C%20preferring%20instead%20to%20take%20their%20chances%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20Yameen%20and%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20(PPM)%20once%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fmaldives-elects-mohamed-muizzu-as-new-president-india-friendly-mohamed-solih-loses%5C%22%3EMaldives%20Elects%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20as%20New%20President%2C%20India-Friendly%20Mohamed%20Solih%20Loses%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20two%20candidates%20in%20the%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20and%20Ibu%20Solih%20%E2%80%93%20were%20seen%20as%20pro-China%20and%20pro-India.%20How%20much%20is%20this%20outcome%20a%20referendum%20on%20the%20two%20countries%3F%20Also%2C%20do%20people%20believe%20that%20Indian%20troop%20presence%20threatens%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20sovereignty%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20of%20foreign%20occupation%20is%20a%20common%20rhetorical%20device%20in%20Maldivian%20history%20and%20politics%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20most%20Maldivians%20genuinely%20fear%20losing%20sovereignty%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20certainly%20been%20looking%20to%20increase%20its%20military%20presence%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20some%20of%20these%20deals%20were%20arranged%20during%20the%20previous%20PPM%20administration%2C%20which%20itself%20had%20no%20qualms%20about%20sovereignty%20when%20amending%20the%20constitution%20to%20allow%20unprecedented%20foreign%20ownership%20of%20land%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20have%2C%20rightly%2C%20been%20unsettled%20by%20the%20Solih%20government%E2%80%99s%20secrecy%20over%20agreements%20with%20the%20Indian%20military%2C%20but%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%20won%E2%80%99t%20continue%20in%20office%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20imagine%20this%20will%20affect%20their%20re-election%20prospects%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia-ibrahim-solih-maldives-presidential-election%5C%22%3EAhead%20of%20Maldives%20Presidential%20Polls%2C%20Solih%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Ties%20With%20India%20Emerge%20as%20Main%20Issue%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20has%20traditionally%20maintained%20its%20independence%20by%20practicing%20balanced%20international%20relations.%20It%20was%20probably%20former%20president%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20previous%20lurch%20to%20the%20east%20that%20prompted%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20scramble%20for%20the%20Maldives%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuizzu%E2%80%99s%20claims%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98pro-Maldives%E2%80%99%20should%20mean%20a%20return%20to%20pragmatism%2C%20including%20recognition%20that%20sinking%20the%20country%20further%20into%20Chinese%20or%20Indian%20debt%20is%20the%20fastest%20way%20to%20cede%20sovereignty%2C%20and%20that%20no%20sane%20leader%20would%20ever%20sever%20ties%20with%20its%20largest%20neighbour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20sentiment%20for%20India%20you%20noticed%20in%20your%20travels%20across%20the%20country%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20xenophobic%20tub-thumping%20of%20a%20few%20politicians%20in%20Male%2C%20individual%20Maldivians%20must%20be%20among%20the%20kindest%20and%20warmest%20people%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20never%20noticed%20any%20specific%20prejudice%20against%20Indians%20during%20my%20time%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20infamous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-swift-justice-protesters-international-yoga-day-event%5C%22%3EYoga%20Day%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20was%20the%20work%20of%20religious%20radicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20tourists%20have%20only%20begun%20to%20represent%20a%20major%20market%20share%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20but%20Maldivians%20have%20been%20raised%20on%20Bollywood%20songs%20and%20Hindi%20soap%20operas%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20well%20as%20depending%20on%20visits%20to%20India%20for%20medical%20care%2C%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20own%20hospitals%20are%20staffed%20by%20Indian%20doctors%2C%20and%20its%20classrooms%20are%20filled%20with%20Indian%20teachers.%20These%20are%20the%20places%20where%20it%20really%20counts%2C%20and%20I%20think%20people-to-people%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives%20will%20always%20be%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20anticipate%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years%20for%20the%20country%20to%20be%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresident%20Solih%20tried%20and%20failed%20to%20tackle%20this%20persistent%20problem%2C%20but%20the%20previous%20PPM%20government%20did%20not%20even%20try.%20There%20was%20strong%20evidence%20of%20official%20collusion%20in%20the%20disappearance%20and%20probable%20murder%20of%20my%20former%20colleague%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.himalmag.com%2Fmaldives-disappeared-journalist-family-waits-for-closure-ahmed-rilwan%2F%5C%22%3EAhmed%20Rilwan%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202014%2C%20and%20those%20eventually%20charged%20have%20already%20been%20released%20to%20house%20arrest%2C%20indicating%20they%20will%20soon%20be%20allowed%20back%20into%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20fear%20the%20next%20five%20years%20will%20bring%20more%20repression%20and%20self-censorship%20now%20that%20radicalised%20gangs%20have%20learned%20they%20can%20act%20with%20impunity.%20I%20also%20fear%20the%20Maldives%20will%20continue%20to%20slip%20back%20into%20the%20same%20state%20of%20stable%20suppression%20it%20experienced%20before%20the%20arrival%20of%20democracy%20in%202008%2C%20forcing%20more%20and%20more%20free%20thinkers%20into%20exile.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientists%20say%20Maldives%20will%20likely%20go%20completely%20underwater%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century.%20Why%20was%20it%20that%20climate%20change%20and%20rising%20sea%20levels%20still%20weren%E2%80%99t%20the%20big%20topics%20of%20debate%20in%20its%20elections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaldivian%20adaptation%20measures%20currently%20include%20modern%20sewerage%20systems%20and%20water%20supplies%20in%20the%20atolls%20as%20well%20as%20a%20switch%20to%20renewables%2C%20which%20have%20become%20a%20standard%20part%20of%20most%20parties%E2%80%99%20development%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20with%20many%20places%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20helplessness%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20such%20a%20huge%20existential%20problem.%20It%E2%80%99s%20one%20that%20political%20systems%20everywhere%20are%20ill-suited%20to%20deal%20with%2C%20particularly%20unstable%20ones%20like%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20concern%20is%20that%20Dhivehi%20civilisation%20faces%20the%20climate%20crisis%20before%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20only%20Maldivians%20can%20decide%20how%20they%20handle%20what%20may%20have%20to%20be%20a%20managed%20decline.%20For%20this%2C%20a%20functioning%20and%20responsive%20democracy%20will%20be%20the%20minimum%20requirement.%20Without%20it%2C%20a%20resort-owning%20elite%20will%20steadily%20leave%20for%20higher%20ground%20overseas%2C%20taking%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20wealth%20with%20them%2C%20and%20leaving%20the%20rest%20to%20their%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696609838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%