as%20she%20exited%20the%20airport%2C%20leaving%20her%20amused.%20The%20co-stars%20were%20seen%20in%20casual%20attire%20and%20took%20selfies%20with%20their%20crew%20before%20leaving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-blushes-as-paparazzi-call-her-jawan-ki-jaan-upon-return-home-from-fighter-shoot-in-italy-with-hrithik-roshan-watch%2Farticleshow%2F104221312.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NewsClick%20Case%3A%20If%20Modi%20Govt%20is%20Really%20Serious%20About%20'Terror%20Financing'%2C%20Why%20Hasn't%20It%20Rung%20the%20US%2C%20China%20and%20FATF%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06222423%2FThe-Wire-31.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20shorter%20version%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2Fnewsclick-despite-terror-financing%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20terrorism%20case%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20its%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20is%20that%20he%20is%20the%20recipient%20of%20funds%20from%20an%20American%20businessman%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%2C%20who%20used%20US-based%20entities%20to%20transfer%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20India%20to%20fuel%20unrest%20aimed%20at%20disrupting%20%E2%80%9Csupplies%20and%20services%20essential%20to%20the%20life%20of%20community%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20Why%3F%20To%20%E2%80%9Cabet%20damage%20and%20destruction%20of%20property%E2%80%9D%2C%20all%20with%20a%20view%20to%20creating%20disaffection%20among%20various%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20%E2%80%9Cactively%20sympathising%20%5Bwith%20a%5D%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ebanned%20terrorist%20organisation%20so%20that%20unity%2C%20integrity%2C%20security%2C%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20country%20can%20be%20threatened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20Singham%20acted%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20China%2C%20since%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20active%20member%20of%20the%20propaganda%20wing%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20two%20Chinese%20telecom%20companies%2C%20Xiaomi%20and%20Vivo%2C%20helped%20execute%20this%20conspiracy%20by%20setting%20up%20%E2%80%9Cthousands%20of%20shell%20companies%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cinfusing%20foreign%20funds%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20police%20have%20arrested%20Purkayastha%20and%20another%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20employee%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20stringent%20anti-terror%20law.%20Phones%20and%20computers%20have%20been%20seized%20from%20over%2050%20other%20individuals%2C%20most%20of%20them%20journalists.%20Without%20going%20into%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20police%20case%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20charges%20themselves%20allows%20us%20to%20raise%20several%20questions%20about%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20seriousness%20in%20unearthing%20and%20prosecuting%20all%20the%20conspirators%20allegedly%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.%20Has%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20requested%20the%20United%20States%20government%20to%20take%20action%20against%20and%2For%20extradite%20its%20citizen%2C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%2C%20whose%20financing%20of%20NewsClick%20is%20being%20called%20a%20terrorist%20crime%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20on%20August%2017%2C%202023%2C%20after%20the%20authorities%20say%20they%20had%20analysed%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20emails%20from%20Purkayastha%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20which%20were%20seized%20two%20years%20earlier%20when%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20first%20raided%20the%20news%20portal%E2%80%99s%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20neither%20before%20or%20after%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed%20does%20the%20government%20appear%20to%20have%20made%20any%20efforts%20to%20even%20interrogate%20Singham%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20accused%20number%203%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20is%20supposedly%20the%20financial%20lynchpin%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECould%20it%20be%20because%20the%20government%20knows%20that%20the%20fund%20transfers%20from%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20entities%20are%20exactly%20what%20both%20the%20remitter%20and%20recipient%20have%20said%20they%20are%3A%20a%20bona%20fide%20investment%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fstatement-on-worldwide-media-holdings-investment-in-newsclick%2Farticle67390484.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20using%20money%20generated%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20And%20that%20if%20India%20were%20to%20request%20the%20US%20authorities%20to%20take%20action%20they%20would%20be%20rebuffed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E2.%20Has%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20notified%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F1fb7278b-2c6e-4e42-9b45-801bd6b8c21a%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMTczZmEifQ.PBNXJqnQKBHgeEYkqjXtgIIV9VR-pvgw3K2feHvkCXU%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F1fb7278b-2c6e-4e42-9b45-801bd6b8c21a%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMTczZmEifQ.PBNXJqnQKBHgeEYkqjXtgIIV9VR-pvgw3K2feHvkCXU%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1696691403262