0all%20dialogue%20with%20Beijing%2C%20since%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20official%20stand%20is%20that%20talks%20and%20terrorism%20cannot%20go%20hand%20in%20hand%3F%20Does%20the%20Modi%20government%20plan%20to%20ask%20China%20to%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20diplomats%20it%20has%20stationed%20in%20India%20because%20the%20Chinese%20side%20%E2%80%93%20according%20to%20the%20police%20charge%20%E2%80%93%20is%20clearly%20interfering%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20internal%20affairs%2C%20just%20as%20India%20has%20accused%20Canadian%20diplomats%20of%20interference%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E4.%20While%20NewsClick%20is%20accused%20of%20indirectly%20receiving%20money%20from%20China%2C%20are%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20the%20NIA%20and%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20going%20to%20now%20open%20UAPA%20and%20money%20laundering%20investigations%20into%20every%20Indian%20company%20that%20has%20received%20direct%20or%20indirect%20Chinese%20investment%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingham%E2%80%99s%20fund%20transfers%20to%20NewsClick%20came%20from%20the%20US%20via%20regular%20banking%20channels%20but%20the%20police%20and%20ED%20say%20the%20funds%20are%20actually%20from%20China%20and%20thus%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity%20and%20integrity.%20Singham%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%20dispute%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20money%20invested%20in%20NewsClick%20is%20%E2%80%98Chinese%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20there%20are%20hundreds%20of%20companies%20in%20India%20that%20have%20actually%20received%20money%20directly%20from%20China-based%20entities%20in%20the%20form%20of%20FDI%2C%20FII%20and%20commercial%20orders.%20Does%20the%20Indian%20government%20intend%20to%20probe%20all%20those%20companies%20and%20seize%20the%20electronic%20devices%20of%20every%20CEO%20and%20promoter%20involved%20so%20that%20their%20emails%20and%20other%20messages%20can%20be%20scrutinised%20for%20evidence%20of%20anti-national%20activity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3