2https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnewsclick-case-if-modi-government-is-really-serious-about-terror-financing-why-havent-they-rung-the-us-china-and-fatf%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Without%20going%20into%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20police%20case%20against%C2%A0'NewsClick'%2C%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20charges%20themselves%20allows%20us%20to%20raise%20several%20questions%20about%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20seriousness%20in%20unearthing%20and%20prosecuting%20all%20the%20conspirators%20allegedly%20involved.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnewsclick-case-if-modi-government-is-really-serious-about-terror-financing-why-havent-they-rung-the-us-china-and-fatf%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India-Maldives%20Ties%20-%20Too%20Strong%20To%20Break%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaldives%20president-elect%20Mohamed%20Muizzu's%20statement%20that%20he%20will%20stick%20to%20his%20campaign%20promise%20to%20remove%20Indian%20troops%20based%20in%20the%20strategically%20important%20archipelago%20nation%20has%20created%20a%20flutter.%20The%20victory%20of%20the%20pro-China%20candidate%20is%20a%20serious%20blow%20to%20India%20in%20its%20geopolitical%20rivalry%20with%20China%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region.%20Muizzu%20ran%20his%20entire%20campaign%20theme%20'India%20Out'%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20an%20alleged%20threat%20to%20the%20Maldives'%20sovereignty%20with%20the%20presence%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20on%20one%20of%20its%20islands.%20Muizzu's%20comments%20were%20aimed%20at%20placating%20China%20and%20provoking%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaldives%2C%20made%20up%20of%201%2C200%20coral%20islands%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20is%20strategically%20located%20on%20the%20main%20shipping%20route%20between%20the%20East%20and%20the%20West.%20Given%20Maldives'%20proximity%20to%20maritime%20trade%20routes%20and%20its%20domestic%20politics%2C%20steeped%20in%20India-China%20rivalry%2C%20the%20latest%20loud%20anti-India%20utterances%20has%20made%20the%20world%20take%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOutgoing%20President%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%20had%20close%20relations%20with%20India.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20had%20defeated%20Abdulla%20Yameen%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20People's%20National%20Congress%2C%20a%20pro-China%20leader%2C%20on%20corruption%20grounds.%20Yameen%20dragged%20Maldives%20into%20China's%20debt%20trap%20diplomacy%20as%20part%20of%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20during%20his%20presidency%20from%202013%20to%202018%2C%20signing%20several%20high-cost%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20lieu%20of%20huge%20debts%20amounting%20to%20around%20%241.4%20billion.%20This%20included%20an%20%24800%20million%20deal%20for%20developing%20the%20main%20international%20airport%20of%20the%20island%20chain%20in%20Male%2C%20which%20was%20awarded%20to%20Chinese%20company%20Beijing%20Urban%20Construction%20Group%20over%20a%20more%20deserving%20Indian%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYameen%20was%20jailed%20for%20money%20laundering%20and%20couldn't%20run%20for%20elections%20against%20Solih%20this%20time.%20So%2C%20he%20propped%20up%20Muizzu%20as%20presidential%20candidate.%20The%20situation%20turned%20worst%20for%20incumbent%20President%20Solih%20after%20a%20split%20in%20his%20ruling%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20which%20saw%20one%20of%20his%20prominent%20party%20leaders%2C%20Mohamed%20Nasheed%2C%20break%20away%2C%20helping%20the%20opposition%20win%20the%20election.%20After%20winning%2C%20Muizzu%20thanked%20his%20political%20mentor%20Yameen%20by%20transferring%20him%20from%20prison%20to%20house%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESolih%2C%20with%20an%20%26quot%3BIndia%20First%26quot%3B%20policy%2C%20initiated%20good%20relations%20with%20New%20Delhi%20in%20response%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%26quot%3BNeighbour%20First%26quot%3B%20policy.%20Many%20infrastructure%20projects%20were%20signed%20as%20part%20of%20this.%20India%20has%20always%20had%20good%20bilateral%20relations%20with%20Maldives%2C%20except%20for%20those%20five%20years%20of%20the%20Yameen%20regime.%20India%20rushed%20assistance%20to%20the%20Maldives%20in%201988%20to%20counter%20the%20coup%20against%20the%20then%20Maldivian%20government.%20Due%20to%20its%20naval%20presence%20in%20the%20region%2C%20India%20was%20the%20first%20to%20help%20Maldives%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20tsunami%20in%202004.%20India%20also%20helped%20the%20nation%20tide%20over%20its%20drinking%20water%20crisis%20in%202014%20and%20provided%20medicines%20as%20part%20Operation%20Sanjeevani.%20In%20January%202021%2C%20when%20developed%20nations%20and%20China%20were%20not%20sharing%20Covid%20vaccines%2C%20India%20sent%20vaccines%20to%20Maldives%20as%20part%20of%20Operation%20Vaccine%20Maitri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20and%20Maldives%20share%20civilisational%20links%20and%20enjoy%20cordial%20and%20multi-dimensional%20relations.%20Maldives%20has%20been%20a%20time-tested%20partner%20of%20India%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region.%20India%20was%20among%20the%20first%20countries%20to%20recognise%20Maldives%20after%20its%20independence%20in%201965%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sandeep%20Tripathi%2C%20founder%2C%20Forum%20for%20Global%20Studies.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20gave%20Lines%20of%20Credit%20to%20the%20Maldives%20multiple%20times%20to%20fund%20its%20myriad%20civilian%2C%20infrastructural%20and%20defence%20projects.%20India%20was%20involved%20in%20developing%20Maldives'%20defence%20infrastructure%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%20The%20Indian%20Navy%20gifted%20naval%20vessels%20for%20coastal%20surveillance%20and%20for%20combating%20drug%20trafficking.%20New%20Delhi%20also%20extended%20aid%20in%20the%20form%20of%20training%20personnel%20and%20capability%20development%2C%20help%20with%20infrastructure%20building%20and%20joint%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20countries%20have%20regularly%20held%20bilateral%20defence%20cooperation%20dialogues%20at%20the%20defence%20secretary%20level%2C%20the%20latest%20in%20March%20in%20Male.%20Tthe%20'Uthuru%20Thila%20Falhu'%20Naval%20Base%2C%20a%20part%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20promote%20regional%20development%20and%20security%2C%20is%20a%20recent%20example%20of%20joint%20work%20on%20developing%20defence%20platforms%20and%20infrastructure%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20Maldives%20collaborated%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20common%20maritime%20security%20concerns%20in%20the%20region.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20biennial%20trilateral%20security%20dialogue%20between%20the%20three%20countries.%20Since%202011%2C%20the%20Colombo%20Security%20Conclave%20has%20acted%20as%20a%20new%20mini-lateral%20organisation%20to%20improve%20security%20cooperation%20with%20the%20island%20and%20coastal%20states%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20new%20in%20the%20India-Maldives%20cooperation%20that%20prompted%20pro-China%20elements%20to%20stir%20up%20an%20anti-India%20tirade%20and%20perception%20among%20the%20people%20of%20Maldives.%20With%20India's%20growing%20stature%20as%20the%20regional%20superpower%2C%20anti-India%20views%20appear%20to%20have%20become%20an%20agenda%20for%20elections%20in%20neighbouring%20countries%20like%20Nepal%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20now%20Maldives.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20this%2C%20India%20must%20not%20lose%20sight%20of%20its%20long-term%20commitment%20to%20help%20Maldives%20in%20its%20overall%20development%2C%20creating%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20common%20people%20in%20that%20country.%20Infrastructure%20and%20projects%20benefiting%20local%20communities%2C%20which%20also%20generate%20employment%20and%20ease%20of%20living%2C%20would%20definitely%20help%20build%20bridges%20with%20the%20country%20and%20its%20people%2C%20with%20whom%20India%20has%20had%20close%20cultural%20and%20traditional%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20High%20Impact%20Community%20Projects%20in%20Maldives%20must%20look%20at%20generating%20employment%2C%20employability%20and%20encourage%20entrepreneurship%20among%20the%20youth.%20India%20should%20also%20look%20at%20the%20timely%20completion%20of%20its%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20Maldives.%20This%20is%20where%20China%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20BRI%20initiatives%2C%20scores%20over%20India.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20electoral%20clatter%20dies%20down%20and%20Muizzu%20officially%20becomes%20President%20on%20November%2017%2C%20the%20practicality%20of%20running%20the%20country%20will%20force%20him%20to%20take%20a%20middle%20path.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Muizzu%20government%20will%20introspect%20India's%20contributions%20over%20the%20last%20so%20many%20years%20and%20tone%20down%20its%20approach%20towards%20New%20Delhi.%20Bilateral%20relations%20do%20not%20take%20a%20U-turn%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Tripathi%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20must%20be%20patient%20and%20adopt%20the%20wait-and-watch%20stance%20without%20cutting%20down%20on%20its%20people-focussed%20outreach%20to%20Maldives.%20There%20are%20no%20permanent%20friends%20or%20enemies%20in%20diplomacy.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20India%20may%20have%20to%20play%20the%20game%20on%20Maldives'%20terms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696605720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fgv2a8qa_mohamed-muizzu-reuters_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-maldives-ties-too-strong-to-break-4457442%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maldives%20president-elect%20Mohamed%20Muizzu's%20statement%20that%20he%20will%20stick%20to%20his%20campaign%20promise%20to%20remove%20Indian%20troops%20based%20in%20the%20strategically%20important%20archipelago%20nation%20has%20created%20a%20flutter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-maldives-ties-too-strong-to-break-4457442%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'We%20Support%20Canada's%20Investigation...%20Into%20This%20Terrible%20Assassination'%2C%20Says%20Senior%20US%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06210233%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJames%20P.%20Rubin%2C%20US%20special%20envoy%20and%20coordinator%20of%20the%20Global%20Engagement%20Center%2C%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Washington%20supports%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20into%20the%20killing%20of%20Canadian%20national%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20that%20it%20urges%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccooperate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fonline-press-briefing-with-james-rubin-special-envoy-and-coordinator-global-engagement-center-gec%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20conference%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fgec-special-report-how-the-peoples-republic-of-china-seeks-to-reshape-the-global-information-environment%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunch%20of%20a%20new%20US%20government%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20China%E2%80%99s%20influence%20networks%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98global%20information%20environment%E2%80%99%2C%20Rubin%20was%20asked%20by%20a%20Canadian%20reporter%20if%20the%20current%20dispute%20between%20Ottawa%20and%20New%20Delhi%20provided%20fertile%20ground%20for%20disinformation%20campaigns%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Eeither%20from%20within%20those%20countries%20or%20from%20the%20outside%E2%80%A6%20%5Band%20makes%5D%20Canada%20a%20more%20attractive%20target%20for%20%5BChinese%5D%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERubin%20heads%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20centre%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20works%20on%20countering%20foreign%20disinformation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctricky%20subject%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20everyone%20to%20help%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%93%20help%20advance%20the%20investigation%20into%20this%20terrible%20assassination%2C%20and%20we%20would%20urge%20everyone%20to%20cooperate%20and%20to%20take%20the%20investigation%20as%20far%20as%20it%20goes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20obviously%20an%20area%20that%20is%20ripe%20for%20information%20manipulation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20any%20specific%20evidence%20of%20the%20Canadian-Indian%20issue%20but%20I%20do%20know%20that%20China%20has%20made%20a%20big%20effort%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20domestic%20affairs%20of%20Canada.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadian-newspapers-react-nijjar-killing-trudeau%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20legislators%20in%20his%20country%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20government%20had%20been%20investigating%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20of%20official%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%2C%20Canada%20had%20announced%20an%20inquiry%20into%20interference%20in%20its%20internal%20affairs%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66745270%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20China%2C%20Russia%20and%20other%20foreign%20actors%3C%2Fa%3E%20driven%20by%20disinformation%20and%20other%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20one%20major%20disinformation%20campaign%20around%20the%20Canada-India%20spat%20is%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20found%20%E2%80%9Cmassive%20amounts%20of%20cocaine%E2%80%9D%20on%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20aircraft%20in%20Delhi%20and%20that%20this%20was%20the%20reason%20his%20departure%20from%20India%20was%20delayed%20by%20two%20days.%20The%20cocaine%20disinformation%20first%20emerged%20on%20Indian%20right%20wing%20social%20media%20handles%20and%20was%20then%20picked%20up%20by%20a%20retired%20Indian%20diplomat%20on%20live%20news%20television%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexdiplomat-claimed-trudeaus-plane-was-full-of-cocaine-during-india-visit-canada-pm-responds-101695991471048.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprompting%20an%20angry%20denial%20by%20the%20Canadian%20authorities.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDescribed%20by%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpro-Khalistani%20terrorist%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nijjar%20was%20killed%20outside%20a%20gurudwara%20in%20Canada%20this%20June%20by%20masked%20gunmen%20and%20New%20Delhi%20has%20dismissed%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20accusation%20of%20involvement%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20ambassador%20to%20Canada%2C%20David%20Cohen%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fshared-intelligence-of-five-eye-partners-informed-trudeaus-allegations-says-us-envoy-to-canada%5C%22%3Ehad%20later%20said%20that%20inputs%20from%20%E2%80%98five%20eyes%E2%80%99%20intelligence%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20led%20to%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20go%20public.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%E2