n_651ee853e4b0bfc227bf9b9d%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fsouthern-airways-express-pilots_n_651ee853e4b0bfc227bf9b9d%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20Sets%20Oct%2010%20as%20Deadline%20for%20Canada%20to%20Reduce%20Diplomatic%20Staff%20in%20India%2C%20Many%20Evacuated%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19022725%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.26.30-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20October%2010%20for%20Canada%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-reiterates-demand-for-canada-to-reduce-diplomatic-staff%5C%22%3Ereduce%20its%20diplomatic%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20to%20match%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%20in%20Canada%2C%20sources%20told%20CTV%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20earlier%20reports%20suggested%20that%2041%20diplomats%20might%20have%20to%20leave%2C%20the%20specific%20request%20is%20for%20parity%20in%20the%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECTV%20News%20has%20learnt%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20Canadian%20diplomats%20working%20in%20India%20outside%20of%20Delhi%20have%20been%20evacuated%20to%20either%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20or%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGlobal%20Affairs%20Canada%20had%20previously%20reported%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20some%20diplomats%20having%20received%20threats%20on%20various%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cassessing%20its%20staff%20complement%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%20and%20out%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20temporarily%20adjust%20staff%20presence%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20department%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20days%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Indian%20government%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20a%20murder%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20initial%20reports%20emerged%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20request%20for%20Canada%20to%20reduce%20its%20diplomats%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20did%20not%20confirm%20the%20demands.%20They%20emphasised%20their%20desire%20to%20avoid%20escalating%20tensions%20with%20India%2C%20noting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cextremely%20challenging%20time%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20diplomats%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20assist%20Canadians%20and%20Canadian%20families.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20taking%20this%20extremely%20seriously%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20engage%20responsibly%20and%20constructively%20with%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Trudeau%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20(October%205)%20briefing%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-reiterates-demand-for-canada-to-reduce-diplomatic-staff%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20mention%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20number%20of%20diplomats%20or%20the%20deadline%20for%20them%20to%20remain%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20get%20into%20the%20details%20of%20diplomatic%20conversations.%20As%20we%20mentioned%2C%20I%20think%20last%20week%2C%20given%20that%20Canadian%20diplomatic%20presence%20is%20very%20much%20higher%2C%20we%20would%20assume%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20reduction.%20I%20think%20that%20broadly%20covers%20those%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20pointed%20out%20that%20Canada%20had%20indicated%20that%20it%20will%20impact%20consular%20services%2C%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6it%E2%80%99s%20up%20to%20the%20Canadian%20side%20who%20they%20choose%20to%20staff%20their%20High%20Commission%20with%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndians%20have%20long%20been%20going%20to%20Canada%20for%20study%20and%20work.%20Around%2040%25%20of%20international%20students%20in%20Canada%20are%20from%20India.%20Further%2C%20Indian%20tourists%20are%20the%20largest%20spenders%20among%20any%20nationality%20as%20per%20a%202021%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Canada%2C%20people%20of%20Indian%20origin%20account%20for%20about%203.7%25%20of%20the%20population%20or%201.4%20million.%20Besides%2C%20770%2C000%20people%20reported%20their%20religion%20as%20Sikhism%2C%20about%202%25%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%2C%20along%20with%20its%20close%20allies%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20have%20repeatedly%20asked%20India%20to%20join%20the%20investigation.%20India%20has%20responded%20that%20it%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20look%20at%20any%20specific%20information%20when%20it%20is%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696598117000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19022725%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.26.30-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fgovt-sets-oct-10-as-deadline-for-canada-to-reduce-diplomatic-staff-in-india-many-evacuated-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20majority%20of%20the%20Canadian%20diplomats%20working%20in%20India%20outside%20of%20Delhi%20have%20been%20evacuated%20to%20either%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20or%20Singapore%2C%20a%20news%20report%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fgovt-sets-oct-10-as-deadline-for-canada-to-reduce-diplomatic-staff-in-india-many-evacuated-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Remove%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material%3A%20Centre%20warns%20X%2C%20YouTube%2C%20Telegram%22