ck-on-cafe-and-shop-kills-at-least-51-people-in-kharkiv-ukraine-says-12977580%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Frussian-rocket-attack-on-cafe-and-shop-kills-at-least-51-people-in-kharkiv-ukraine-says-12977580%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Frussian-rocket-attack-on-cafe-and-shop-kills-at-least-51-people-in-kharkiv-ukraine-says-12977580%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Why%20Me%3F%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20Patients%20of%20Spinal%20Muscular%20Atrophy%20Want%20India%20to%20Learn%20About%20Their%20Condition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20say%20that%20I%20could%20walk%20as%20a%20toddler%20but%20over%20time%2C%20I%20started%20losing%20balance.%20I%20would%20fall%20over%2C%20my%20spine%20became%20slightly%20curved%2C%20and%20I%20needed%20assistance%20with%20daily%20activities.%20My%20parents%20ran%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20get%20a%20diagnosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20recounts%20Priya%20Srivastava%2C%20a%20Lucknow-based%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20disability%20rights%20activist%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20has%20Spinal%20Muscular%20Atrophy%20(SMA)%20Type-II.%20Such%20is%20the%20story%20of%20many%20people%20with%20the%20rare%2C%20progressive%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20when%2014-month-old%20Roha%20began%20experiencing%20trouble%20breathing%2C%20her%20parents%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20another%20town.%20After%20two%20weeks%2C%20multiple%20tests%20and%20misdiagnoses%20later%2C%20they%20were%20shattered%20to%20know%20that%20their%20little%20daughter%20had%20the%20fatal%20illness.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20they%20heard%20of%20SMA%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20meant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%20(RPwD%20Act%2C%202016)%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20include%20SMA%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20not%20much%20awareness%20of%20the%20condition%20even%20among%20medical%20professionals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaran%20Shah%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20canine%20and%20feline%20behaviourist%2C%20was%20misdiagnosed%20with%20polio%20shortly%20after%20birth.%20However%2C%20he%20got%20a%20diagnosis%20after%20his%20mother%20insisted%20on%20getting%20him%20tested%20for%20the%20condition.%20He%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Pawsitivve%20Future%2C%20a%20canine%20training%20centre%2C%20and%20lives%20with%20SMA%20Type-III.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20such%20a%20drastic%20impact%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20get%20to%20know%20more%20about%20this%20condition%20that%20creates%20significant%20impairment%20and%20results%20in%20a%20locomotor%20disability.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295507%2Fdisability-inclusive-policy-at-workplaces-lessons-from-accenture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAwareness%20is%20the%20first%20step%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20help%20the%20cause%20in%20various%20capacities%2C%20including%20raising%20funds%20for%20its%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201075px)%20100vw%2C%201075px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221075%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20there's%20no%20cure%20for%20SMA%2C%20several%20treatments%20have%20been%20suggested%20to%20make%20the%20condition%20less%20disabling%20for%20those%20who%20live%20with%20it.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168.jpg%201075w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22716%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20cure%20for%20SMA%2C%20several%20treatments%20have%20been%20suggested%20to%20make%20the%20condition%20less%20disabling%20for%20those%20who%20live%20with%20it.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20SMA%20and%20whom%20does%20it%20affect%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESMA%20is%20a%20genetic%20condition%20that%20impacts%20the%20control%20of%20muscle%20movement.%20It%20mainly%20affects%20the%20spinal%20region%20while%20the%20muscles%20of%20peripheral%20internal%20organs%20are%20relatively%20unaffected.%20SMA%20is%20a%20progressive%20condition%20that%20ultimately%20leads%20to%20muscle%20wastage%20or%20atrophy%20in%20the%20body.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20globally%2C%201%20in%20every%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnceh%2Fdls%2Fnsmbb_sma.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSpinal%2520Muscular%2520Atrophy%2520(SMA)%2520is%2Cbeing%2520unable%2520to%2520make%2520protein.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10%2C000%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20SMA%2C%20while%20in%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asterhospitals.in%2Fblogs-events-news%2Faster-cmi-bangalore%2Fspinal-muscular-atrophy-types-symptoms-and-treatment%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSMA%2520is%2520a%2520relatively%2520rare%2Caround%25203%252C200%2520newborns%2520every%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3%2C200%20infants%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20born%20with%20the%20condition%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mda.org%2Fdisease%2Fspinal-muscular-atrophy%2Fcauses-inheritance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMuscular%20Dystrophy%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SMA%20is%20caused%20by%20missing%20or%20mutated%20SMN1%20or%20SMN2%20genes%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20survival%20muscle%20neuron%20genes.%20The%20protein%20produced%20by%20this%20gene%20%E2%80%94%20SMN%20protein%20%E2%80%94%20facilitates%20movement%20and%20is%20needed%20by%20motor%20neurons%20to%20function%20effectively.%20Since%20the%20gene%20is%20faulty%20or%20missing%2C%20it%20impedes%20movement%20among%20those%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20SMA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311815%2Fkerala-woman-with-disability-rejected-from-jobs-launched-organic-food-biz-geetha-saleesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindividuals%20experience%20several%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20voluntary%20movements%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20the%20head%2C%20neck%2C%20and%20limbs.%20Priya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20spinal%20cord%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20are%20affected%2C%20people%20with%20SMA%20also%20develop%20scoliosis%20or%20spinal%20curvature.%20I%20have%20it%20too%20and%20I%20manage%20it%20by%20stuffing%20a%20lot%20of%20cushions%20around%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20limited%20mobility%2C%20I%20have%20low%20muscle%20tone%20which%20results%20in%20weaker%20bone%20health%20and%20density.%20Even%20lifting%20a%20book%20seems%20like%20a%20Herculean%20task%20to%20me.%20My%20condition%20also%20makes%20me%20prone%20to%20frequent%20fractures%20and%20joint