ed%20to%20support%20it%2C%20the%20money%20was%20an%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFinancial%20stress%20became%20even%20harder%20when%20Mahan%E2%80%99s%20father%20passed%20away.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20completing%20my%20graduation%20and%20was%20heartbroken.%20However%2C%20I%20also%20had%20to%20look%20after%20my%20family.%20Studying%20further%20was%20out%20of%20the%20question%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20agriculture%20like%20my%20father%20for%20a%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20said%20that%20one%20cannot%20stop%20a%20curious%20mind.%20Mahan%20could%20have%20decided%20to%20go%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F265977%2Fharyana-farmer-mushroom-laddu-sweets-jam-pickles-earns-lakhs-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20traditional%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20instead%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20research%20alongside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20loved%20reading%20and%20I%20would%20go%20online%20to%20look%20for%20papers%20on%20farming%20and%20seed%20saving.%20I%20read%20articles%20and%20papers%20on%20how%20there%20are%20many%20indigenous%20rice%20varieties%20that%20are%20going%20extinct.%20I%20also%20noticed%20while%20India%20has%20lots%20of%20resources%20in%20agriculture%2C%20no%20one%20was%20trying%20to%20save%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%202008%2C%20Mahan%20had%20already%20started%20to%20set%20up%20a%20%E2%80%98rice%20library%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20testimony%20of%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20heritage%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20days%20he%20spent%20on%20the%20field%20with%20his%20father%2C%20Mahan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThose%20were%20the%20best%20days%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20used%20to%20do%20everything%20from%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20cattle%20and%20sowing%20the%20seeds.%20The%20seed%20ba